id: pm-mf4j
title: Add pm config set positional value form and shorten the invalid config-key error
description: "Agent-UX polish (subset of pm-5k2w M5). (1) pm config set <key> <value> now accepts the value positionally and routes it to the correct typed flag (--policy/--format/--criterion) by key, with off/on/true/false -> disabled/enabled synonyms for boolean policy keys; the typed-flag forms still work and conflicting flag+positional is a clear error. (2) The invalid config-key error now lists only the ~21 canonical kebab keys plus '(underscore variants also accepted)' instead of all ~45 kebab+snake forms, cutting token cost for agents. Pure routing logic in src/core/config/positional-value.ts (100% covered); MCP+SDK contract parity added. Implemented by config-ux-subagent under pm-5k2w."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
tags[5]: agent-ux,cli,config,polish,token-efficiency
